10... Nf6 11. f3
{ While developing we always prioritize protecting our hanging material, either by defending our pieces or by taking our opponent's ones whenever possible. }
11... Be7 12. Nc5 Qe5 13. Qd4
{ White is ahead in both space and piece placement. After castling long, we can use the d-file to put pressure on Black's position, making them suffer. }
