{ White's pieces are doing better than Black's! Our rooks are placed on the perfect squares and the Bh3 is very annoying with the pin on d7. We are still keeping our space advantage as Black's ...d5 is not possible for now, and so the Nb6 and Ba6 are still doing badly. }
