11... Be7
{ The more logical move! Black really needs to get out of the center.   11...d5  doesn't stop us at all!  12.Bb2  d4  13.O-O-O± }
12. Bb2 d5 13. O-O-O c6 14. g4
{ And Shirov won a very nice game that I fully recommend you guys learn! Shirov-Kuderinov, Khanty-Mansiysk 2005. }
